@page "/"

@* Placeholder landing page — the first routable @page, so the shell (NavBar /
   drawer / StatusBar) finally has something to host. The season grid, watchlist
   and notifications land in later phases. The "type check" panel exercises all
   four font slots and can be removed once real content lands. *@

<AppPageTitle />

<section class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-6 py-10">
    <header class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-base-content">
            Anime Feed Manager
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Track and manage your anime season library. This is a placeholder home page —
            the season grid, watchlist and notifications arrive in later phases.
        </p>
    </header>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-base-content bg-base-100 p-5 text-sm shadow-brutal">
        <p class="mb-3 font-display text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-base-content/50">
            Type check
        </p>
        <dl class="grid grid-cols-[7rem_1fr] gap-y-2">
            <dt class="text-base-content/50">Display</dt>
            <dd class="font-display">Space Grotesk — Spring 2026</dd>

            <dt class="text-base-content/50">Body</dt>
            <dd class="font-sans">Inter — the quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</dd>

            <dt class="text-base-content/50">Mono</dt>
            <dd class="font-mono">SF Mono — 12 eps · 23:59:47 · v5</dd>

            <dt class="text-base-content/50">Japanese</dt>
            <dd class="font-ja text-lg">日本語のタイトル — 進撃の巨人</dd>
        </dl>
    </div>
</section>
